{"tid":524254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[9/1]血庫存量降至警戒水平　紅會籲即往捐血　3捐血站延長服務至晚上8時","createTime":"2018-01-09T11:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T02:00:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"045a12fdac5f4557f57f70b3ac32a759081c2420","tid":524254,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T11:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180109/s00001/8863c480a39d8303b1a1a92d843acd80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180109%2Fs00001%2F8863c480a39d8303b1a1a92d843acd80.jpg&h=5a36536c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港紅十字會輸血服務中心表示，全港醫院血液使用量一直高企，但捐血人數已長時間未達標，目前血庫各類血型血液的存量，均已下降至警戒水平，呼籲市民立即前往捐血。中心已延長銅鑼灣、荃灣和觀塘捐血站的每天服務時間至晚上8時。<br />\n<br />\n中心指，全港醫院的內科病牀使用率上升，血液需求現時處於極高水平，但捐血人數長期未達每天1100人的目標，剛過去的聖誕新年長假期亦減低市民捐血意欲，昨日捐血人數只有852人，致血液收集量不理想，呼籲市民立即捐血，以維持穩定的血液供應予醫院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180109/s00001/1515493438423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180109%2Fs00001%2F1515493438423&d=F3zW9SDv6pnO7cLvCRtNYf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6c870e88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180109%2Fs00001%2F1515493438423&h=0ae383ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180109/s00001/1515493438423</a>"},{"pid":"3bc71c32b5ae096871d7e0646e3883a9864b5bc4","tid":524254,"uid":7168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce04a0c8c087122210fc85a2f76bac9cca3fcaf","tid":524254,"uid":80461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"重有852人捐，咁撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":